    "extra_descs": [
      {
        "desc": "   Um, ok just a small zone, with only 16 rooms, 12 mobs, and 10 objects. It\nis based on a jungle, and was designed to join to a forest area at room\n1000\n\nIt is not finished, I started building it for a Mud that never realy got\nof the ground, so I thought I would tidy it up a little and upload it to\nthe circleMud ftp site.  If you want to use it as it is, or even add more\nto it, feel free to do so.  If you use it just send me a quick E-mail to\nlet me know.\n\nMartin Winning,\niwinning@@proweb.co.uk\n\np.s  If you are looking for a builder, I need somewhere to build :)-\n     gimmie a mail at the above address.\nLinks: 00n",
        "keywords": [
          "credits",
          "info"
        ]
      }
    ],
